\n勇武先可以升級武力對抗<br />\n我地要再一次話比人聽<br />\n和理同勇武唔會割蓆<br />\n我地既民意不跌反升<br />\n和平遊行係無用<br />\n但係和平遊行既人數會係我地每次遊行既手牌<br />\n話比全世界知我地試左數以百萬計人和平遊行<br />\n但係政府漠視民意，官迫民反<br />\n迫我地使用暴力抗爭"},{"pid":"21c4ccf40e30eccc2f83b2d960ed8f6479c9b3c8","tid":1475651,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:35:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">818銅鑼灣見</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J61W6fj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ61W6fj.gif&h=ddc82ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHsJHkY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHsJHkY.gif&h=fe893bbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n816都有野做架<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P1YfoZY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP1YfoZY.png&h=418d03ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/15/223112_831243870f9171a3425ed2272ee528aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F15%2F223112_831243870f9171a3425ed2272ee528aa.png&h=540b6092&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/15/223114_ddb1d7a34fe15702af70f93e7eab0fc1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F15%2F223114_ddb1d7a34fe15702af70f93e7eab0fc1.png&h=920edcaa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0aeb5bfdefab174e2f74b13846d863961eb9573","tid":1475651,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:35:34.000Z","msg":"理想係咁樣<br />\n<br />\n但講定先都得 實際應該唔得<br />\n講定先係避免到時又互屌同割席<br />\n<br />\n唔得既原因係唔批通知書<br />\n到時人多 一定會塞曬出維園外<br />\n到時黑警會專登挑釁同對示威者動武<br />\n而示威者即使只係自衛 但場面已經唔會可以和平<br />\n<br />\n我覺得以上事情9成會出現<br />\n所以到時唔好怪和理非唔倒 因為根本唔係示威者控制倒"},{"pid":"8370148d31493d1971e28895eb48e7759937c1d2","tid":1475651,"uid":24048,"